TestSuite 'Verifica o pagamento do funcionario'

TestCase 'Verifica se EMP-OT-RATE é 0.25 para 40 horas'
MOVE 40 TO EMP-HOURS
MOVE 23.50 TO EMP-HOURLY-RATE
PERFORM B200-PAYMENT-WEEKLY
EXPECT EMP-OT-RATE TO BE 0.25

TestCase 'Verifica se EMP-OT-RATE é 0.50 para 50 horas'
MOVE 50 TO EMP-HOURS
MOVE 23.50 TO EMP-HOURLY-RATE
PERFORM B200-PAYMENT-WEEKLY
EXPECT EMP-OT-RATE TO BE 0.50

TestCase 'Verifica se o pagamento semanal (EMP-PAY-WEEK) é >= 900 para 40 horas'
MOVE 40 TO EMP-HOURS
MOVE 23.50 TO EMP-HOURLY-RATE
PERFORM B200-PAYMENT-WEEKLY
EXPECT EMP-PAY-WEEK >= 900

TestCase 'Verifica se o pagamento mensal (EMP-PAY-MONTH) é >= 9600 para 160 horas'
MOVE 160 TO EMP-HOURS
MOVE 1600 TO EMP-PAY-WEEK
PERFORM B300-PAYMENT-MONTHLY
EXPECT EMP-PAY-MONTH >= 9600
